{
  "stem": "14552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were overseeing that we should not take any liberties in any which way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Auschwitz from April till, I think, the end of November.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the Russians were advancing-- is what we heard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, also, I have a method is that while we were in Auschwitz, we were handed postcards to send to people we know that we are-- it was pre-written-- that we are well and, and regards.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was-- that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We also heard-- I don't know how, how this came about, that the Russians were advancing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we were herded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we marched for days and days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every day, we were marching away from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not put into any cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, towards-- away from the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, on the way, whoever couldn't keep up was shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the food was-- I don't-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember getting food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember that my, my knees were locking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I-- it wasn't any more a, a, a reflex.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't put my foot out in front of me unless I thought very carefully to put it out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we sat overnight someplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next day, again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many, many people died on that march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we were taken to a, a munition factory, to Hainichen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hainichen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "H-E-I-N-E-C-H-E-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw a documentary about Hainichen a half a year ago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, oh my god.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is the place where I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a, a, a big building they have allocated for these prisoners.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we worked in an ammunition factory 12 hours, either at nighttime or daytime.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They exchanged it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
